nsent due to a loophole in the Dominican Republic's law. However, she realizes that she forgot her passport and so asks Dorota for help. Serena, Chuck, Nate reluctantly team up with Georgina to find Blair, until Georgina gets a tip from one of her sources and she leaves. Georgina then, as Gossip Girl, informs Louis and Sophia of Blair's location. Nate, Serena and Chuck eventually find Blair in a hotel room with Dan. Sophia finds Blair and threatens to forcefully sell Eleanor's company as dowry if Blair chooses not to return, on which Blair reluctantly decides to go back. Elsewhere, Nate has another meeting with the real Charlie Rhodes, who goes by the name of Lola. At the end, it is implied that neither Chuck nor Serena, who takes the blame, leaked the video of Blair confessing her love for Chuck. It is revealed that Georgina is simply filling in for Gossip Girl ever since she abandoned the blog after Chuck and Blair's car accident.\n----\n'''Title reference:''' The 2010 film ''[[The Back-up Plan]]''.\n |LineColor=FF5F5F\n}}\n{{Episode list/sublist|Gossip Girl (season 5)\n |EpisodeNumber= 102\n |EpisodeNumber2= 15\n |Title= Crazy, Cupid, Love\n |WrittenBy= Austin Winsberg\n |DirectedBy= [[Matt Penn]]\n |OriginalAirDate= {{Start date|2012|2|13}}\n |Aux4= 1.13<ref name=\"low\">{{cite web|last=Seidman |first=Robert |url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2012/02/07/monday-final-ratings-the-voice-alcatraz-house-two-and-a-half-men-adjusted-up/119033/ |title=Monday Final Ratings: 'The Voice,' 'Alcatraz,' 'House,' 'Two and a Half Men' Adjusted Up |website=TV by the Numbers |date=February 7, 2012 |accessdate=February 7, 2012 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120209211614/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2012/02/07/monday-final-ratings-the-voice-alcatraz-house-two-and-a-half-men-adjusted-up/119033/ |archivedate=February 9, 2012}}</ref>\n |ShortSummary= It's Valentine's Day on the Upper East Side and Blair cannot resist playing Cupid for someone she lov