iivm.forter.ro/istoric| title =ISTORICUL CENTRULUI DE INSTRUIRE PENTRU INFANTERIE SI V\u00c2NATORI DE MUNTE| last =| first =| date = | website = bivm.forter.ro| publisher =| access-date =9 March 2020| quote = }}</ref>\n\n== Russia==\n[[File:RIAN archive 188831 A mountain outpost.jpg|thumb|right|Trooper of the now disbanded 33rd Mountain Brigade in Dagestan, 2008]]\n* [[7th Guards Mountain Air Assault Division|7th Guards Airborne Assault Division (Mountain)]] (''7-\u044f \u0433\u0432\u0430\u0440\u0434\u0435\u0439\u0441\u043a\u0430\u044f \u0434\u0435\u0441\u0430\u043d\u0442\u043d\u043e-\u0448\u0442\u0443\u0440\u043c\u043e\u0432\u0430\u044f \u0434\u0438\u0432\u0438\u0437\u0438\u044f (\u0433\u043e\u0440\u043d\u0430\u044f) -  7-ya Gvardeyskaya Desantno-Shturmovaya Diviziya (Gornaya)'')<ref>{{cite web|url=https://structure.mil.ru/structure/forces/airborne/structure/details.htm?id=11270@egOrganization|title=7th Guards Airborne Assault (Mountain) Order of the Red Banner Order of Kutuzov 2nd Class Division|website=Structure.mil.ru|accessdate=29 January 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bratishka.ru/specnaz/vdv/6.php|title=\u0416\u0443\u0440\u043d\u0430\u043b \u0434\u043b\u044f \u0441\u043f\u0435\u0446\u043d\u0430\u0437\u0430 \u00ab\u0411\u0440\u0430\u0442\u0438\u0448\u043a\u0430\u00bb \u2014 \u0421\u0442\u0440\u0443\u043a\u0442\u0443\u0440\u0430 \u0412\u0414\u0412|website=Bratishka.ru|accessdate=29 January 2019|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6ENJpP51q?url=http://www.bratishka.ru/specnaz/vdv/6.php|archive-date=12 February 2013|url-status=dead}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://sdrvdv.ru/7-ya-gvardejskaya-desantno-shturmovaya-gornaya-krasnoznamennaya-ordena-kutuzova-2-j-stepeni-diviziya/|title=7-\u044f \u0433\u0432\u0430\u0440\u0434\u0435\u0439\u0441\u043a\u0430\u044f \u0434\u0435\u0441\u0430\u043d\u0442\u043d\u043e-\u0448\u0442\u0443\u0440\u043c\u043e\u0432\u0430\u044f (\u0433\u043e\u0440\u043d\u0430\u044f) \u041a\u0440\u0430\u0441\u043d\u043e\u0437\u043d\u04